This software is developed and distributed for educational, research, and
personal experimentation purposes only. HackMate automates the generation of
OpenCore EFI configurations and is intended to assist users in learning about
bootloader configuration, ACPI tables, kernel extensions, and macOS
compatibility on non-Apple hardware.

The authors do not encourage, endorse, or facilitate any violation of software
license agreements, intellectual property rights, or applicable laws. Users are
solely and entirely responsible for ensuring that their use of this software
complies with all applicable laws, regulations, and third-party terms of
service in their jurisdiction.

